attributes.description:
Current selection. Single mode: the chosen value as a string;
empty string = nothing selected. Multiple mode: space-separated
values.

tags.description:
Visual + semantic divider. Horizontal (default) or vertical;
optional centre glyph (hex / dot / none). `decorative` switches
between role=separator and role=presentation.

Determinate progress indicator. role="progressbar";
aria-valuemin / max / now reflect state. `indeterminate` mode
animates a sliding ribbon when the percent isn't known.

Menu bar — managed keyboard navigation across a row of dropdown
triggers. role="menubar"; arrow keys move focus between triggers;
Home / End jump.

Inline callout for notes, tips, warnings, and errors. The `tone`
attribute drives both the accent colour and the leading icon;
`label` adds an uppercase header above the slotted body.
